<br>
I don't know what level you would have to be to do that camp with a group, but if you could do it with a group and get experience from it, it might not be so bad as an experience camp that gives the chance at a charm. (a nice ring with regent conserve 3 dropped also and a nice mantle for rangers, sham, etc)  I never did see the charm in the 4 named mobs I killed in the course of about 60 hours spent there.  I did get about 6AA points though.(roughly).<br>
<br>
So, if you can get experience camping a charm, then do it but if your not going to be getting good experience, then don't waste the time, just level up and get the one from PoP.<br>
